OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening and night with plenty of
OL,7,Fclear spells. Some low cloud
OL,8,Fdeveloping over the hills during the
OL,9,Fearly hours but remaining dry. Staying
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudier this morning with a
OL,13,Ffew spots of rain likely, before
OL,14,Fclearing eastwards. Skies brightening
OL,15,Fby lunchtime, with plenty of sunshine
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Generally feeling fresher
OL,17,Fthan of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
